    <item>
      <title>黎巴嫩与以色列冲突加剧 面临停电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/lebanon-suffers-from-total-blackout-as-clashes-with-israel-intensify</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于真主党和以色列之间的跨境袭击愈演愈烈，国营电力公司表示其天然气已经耗尽，黎巴嫩全国陷入“全面停电”困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/lebanon-suffers-from-total-blackout-as-clashes-with-israel-intensify</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 15:21:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“高昂”住房成本给民主党带来压力 促使哈里斯提出 25,000 美元税收抵免法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/kamala-harris-housing-plan-targets-gen-z-millennial-voters-hurt-by-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡马拉·哈里斯承诺采取行动降低住房成本，这一举措降低了年轻人、少数族裔和低收入选民等民主党核心选民对总统竞选的热情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/kamala-harris-housing-plan-targets-gen-z-millennial-voters-hurt-by-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赤道几内亚领导人任命前银行家解决经济危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/equatorial-guinea-leader-taps-ex-banker-to-fix-economic-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赤道几内亚任命曼努埃尔·奥萨·恩苏埃·恩苏埃为总理。三周前，该国因上届政府未能解决该国经济困境而将其解职。]]></description>
