      <title>真主党在致命袭击后向以色列发射导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/hezbollah-fires-missile-barrage-at-israel-after-deadly-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[真主党称，这是自 10 个多月前双方开始交火以来，对黎巴嫩发动的最致命的袭击之一，随后真主党向以色列北部发射了多枚火箭弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/hezbollah-fires-missile-barrage-at-israel-after-deadly-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 11:17:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
