      <title>以色列盟友阿塞拜疆在伊朗试射导弹后举行防空演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/israel-ally-azerbaijan-holds-air-defense-drills-after-iran-tests</link>
